snippet.title: Rhythm Doctor - Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
"Just press space on the 7th beat."

Browser demo: http://fizzd.itch.io/rhythm-doctor

Vote for us on Steam Greenlight please! Link coming once we actually put it up in an hour lol. (if you found this right now, shhh! stay quiet for now)

OK it's here: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=886344577

Steam's about to close Greenlight any moment now. You can do it, game entry!

Update 10 days later: woohoo you did it, game entry! thank you for your support people, it's all thanks to you :)
